Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.00,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就要生下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.94,0:00:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是生小孩也要注意 還是有危險性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.44,0:00:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那個沒關係啦 我現在很辛苦阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.22,0:00:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是啦 當男生真好不用受這種苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.39,0:00:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生也很苦阿 哪裡  很多阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.70,0:00:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是不能上床阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.88,0:00:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳可不可以用嘴巴幫我阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.98,0:01:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼阿 我可是孕婦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.16,0:01:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是啦 如果嘴巴不行的話 用手也可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啦 好噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.27,0:01:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在沒心情碰你 一想到就噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.08,0:01:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那麽麼嚴重吧 男生如果太忍耐會死喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.25,0:01:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講什麼傻話阿 總之不行不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.83,0:01:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我看A片打手槍喔 你不是經常在打嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.74,0:02:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很噁心耶 你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們即將迎接第一個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.05,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是懷孕中的妻子沒有性慾 我只好狂看A片打手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.26,0:02:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像很看不起我這樣 但男人也是有很多苦衷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也體諒一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.78,0:02:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆的姐姐帮我做家事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.52,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有天老婆在睡覺 老婆的姐姐說 想來家裡幫忙做家事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就來我們家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.47,0:03:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 出門被小孩絆住 應該可以更早來的 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我老公不可靠阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你不可靠才要麻煩姐姐 你道歉阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太也很認真工作阿 對吧 純太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.10,0:03:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐抱歉 給你添麻煩了 真想快點看到小寶寶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.71,0:03:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐跟老婆不一樣 有種成熟的魅力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.92,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又成熟又溫柔又善解人意 這兩個人真的是姐妹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.33,0:04:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為姐姐跟老婆睡 我就睡沙發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.57,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙發就是我的床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.88,0:04:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐真的美人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.72,0:04:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太什麼都要我做 真像個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.64,0:04:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過純太也在忍耐吧 哪有 他都看A片打手槍阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒在忍耐阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就原諒他嘛 他還這麼年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.29,0:05:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打手槍都發出阿阿的聲音 我要不注意都難阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.37,0:05:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他都以為我沒注意到 叫成那樣誰不注意阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.25,0:05:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明美這種事情不用跟姐報告吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你都聽到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.66,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼我聽到 這種話題太隱私了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.30,0:05:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種話題 什麼話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.41,0:05:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種話題是什麼話題阿 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.68,0:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太 那種話題是什麼 我不懂耶 你告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是打手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.63,0:06:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈 好丟臉喔 這種事不要大聲嚷嚷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.84,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是妳先說的 我都聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.08,0:06:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太結婚後變的好噁心 不害燥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.65,0:06:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.29,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦 明美 妳太欺負人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐 她最近都這樣阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.84,0:06:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 我會好好跟她談的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.18,0:07:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過純太 越吵咸情會越好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.55,0:07:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎 當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.16,0:07:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很羨慕你們唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.20,0:07:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明美真叫人火大 相較起來 姐姐好溫柔喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.12,0:07:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明美怎麼可以跟姐說那些阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.20,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我也該反省啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.91,0:08:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐到底會怎麼跟她說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.56,0:08:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.37,0:08:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次看到姐姐穿睡衣 比白天大膽很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.54,0:08:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛太生氣沒注意到 姐姐好性感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.83,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐真的好性感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明美生宝宝的时候我还要工作 姐姐一起去真是幫了太忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.86,0:13:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要好好答謝姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.88,0:13:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然想到今晚只有我跟姐兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.09,0:13:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一想到姐在裡面睡覺 我就無法冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能打手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚇我一跳 原來是去廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.56,0:14:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐不知道有沒有穿內褲 真養眼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著我的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.35,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想像一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.66,0:15:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像變大了喔 姐妳在幹麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.71,0:15:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.72,0:16:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在摸奇怪的地方 奇怪的地方是指哪裡阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法說明阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.34,0:16:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我幫你回答吧 難雞很痛對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.93,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來幫你吧 痛到受不了了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.90,0:17:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有反應喔 硬梆梆的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.69,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛的雞雞 我要多親幾下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.15,0:18:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很有成覺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.33,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.30,0:19:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好好吃喔 純太的雞雞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.86,0:19:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看我怎麼吃你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.52,0:20:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舒服嗎 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃至極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.84,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想讓我的小穴一樣舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.15,0:21:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦呢 變的好熱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.33,0:21:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐我快忍不住了 什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.58,0:21:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行是指什麼阿 告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.86,0:21:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出來了 什麼要出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.20,0:21:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是熱熱白白的那個嗎 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.08,0:22:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看阿 能射多少呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.42,0:22:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.16,0:22:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個可愛雞雞快點射給我看阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.63,0:22:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.85,0:22:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.26,0:22:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射的到處都是呢 還能再射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.02,0:23:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.82,0:23:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能阿 只是想像雞雞都要爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.26,0:24:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為什麼要這麼緊張呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.80,0:24:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全睡不著阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.44,0:24:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和姐姐一起生活真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.75,0:24:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和明美不同 有種男人和女人生活的真實感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.73,0:25:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太 要上班了嗎 我幫你做了便當喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.44,0:25:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.46,0:25:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿睡衣的姐姐好性成 穿圍裙的姐姐也讓人心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.24,0:26:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太 工作加油喔 謝謝 下班打給我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.22,0:26:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去看小寶寶吧 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.26,0:26:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 視缐停留留在奶子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.84,0:26:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐好像變成我老婆 我們好像結婚了一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.01,0:26:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓人好振奮阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.65,0:26:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘記带組姐做的便當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.96,0:26:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到車站才想到 一定會遲到的 但现在没心思管這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.43,0:26:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好想吃姐做的便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.79,0:27:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為了拿姐的便當回家 但看到的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.47,0:28:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一句話也說不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:35.24,0:33:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馱只有在A片裡看過女生自慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.31,0:33:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是像姐姐這樣 不是演戲的 我第一次看到 真是好震驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.88,0:34:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才真是太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.32,0:34:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常媽媽在根本不能這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:01.93,0:35:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.37,0:35:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.55,0:35:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會是純太吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.06,0:35:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這天 和姐姐看完寶寶  一起去喝了點酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.30,0:35:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後還在家裡繼續喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.41,0:36:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.12,0:36:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寶寶和純太好像喔 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:10.13,0:36:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是因為是女生 跟我長的像好像有點可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.57,0:36:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寶寶果然可愛阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.61,0:36:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想再生一個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:34.88,0:36:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐還那麼年輕 再生一個也不遲阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.23,0:36:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能吧 因為都沒在做那檔事阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.44,0:36:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:58.41,0:37:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 當然是做愛阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:09.55,0:37:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐那麼漂亮 我很羨慕大哥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:23.50,0:37:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有純太說我漂亮而以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.84,0:37:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他都不跟我做喔 完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.76,0:37:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纯太也是做了愛才有小孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:01.94,0:38:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明美高潮後才有小孩對吧 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.25,0:38:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟明美都怎麼做愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.86,0:38:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一週兩次 三次 還是每夫都做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.60,0:38:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没有狠多次 明美懷孕後都不想要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.12,0:38:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說我想要 她都說我噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.83,0:39:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那跟我做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.18,0:39:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以妳中午一個人做了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.41,0:39:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為姐姐也是欲求不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.56,0:39:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到姐姐自慰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.97,0:39:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 姐―睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.14,0:39:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.65,0:39:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種地放睡着 會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.43,0:40:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍不住啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.04,0:40:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 嗯 妳喝了這麼多阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.21,0:40:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.34,0:41:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.95,0:41:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.26,0:41:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.37,0:41:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 起來阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.32,0:42:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.15,0:42:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的睡著了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.13,0:43:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐沒穿內衣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:11.01,0:44:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.35,0:47:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:21.20,0:47:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 快起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:04.57,0:48:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐 快起來 回房睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.72,0:48:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:26.50,0:48:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:34.57,0:48:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.58,0:48:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再一次 把頭放到枕頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:46.62,0:48:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太 我的秘密曝光了 沒關係的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:04.67,0:49:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐 是我阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:09.21,0:49:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天來個久違的性愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.78,0:51:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會痛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:14.56,0:51:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要 真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:14.59,0:52:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:19.26,0:52:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好會舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:51.96,0:52:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.17,0:54:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:12.78,0:54:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:12.93,0:56:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.41,0:56:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:37.92,0:56:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你磨蹭什麼 快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:48.10,0:56:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:24.13,0:57:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:28.14,0:57:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:42.02,0:57:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等你在做什麼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:53.53,0:57:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麽了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:58.47,0:58:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是姐姐要我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:02.14,0:58:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 怎麽這様
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:05.21,0:58:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:48.32,0:58:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:49.79,0:58:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:53.89,0:58:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等不要 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:01.66,0:59:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 這什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:21.65,0:59:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 請住手 快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:27.02,0:59:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.43,0:59:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:42.24,0:59:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 真的不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:48.31,0:59:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:52.95,0:59:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你在幹麻 快住手 都興奮了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:03.69,1:00:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:09.53,1:00:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行阿 好濕阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:27.18,1:00:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好激烈阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:42.26,1:00:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.74,1:00:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:01.48,1:01:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不行阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:07.29,1:01:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 快住手 姐姐不要怕 我讓妳舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:30.41,1:01:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:34.32,1:01:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:37.92,1:01:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手放開何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.90,1:01:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很舒服吧 討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:02.94,1:02:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.02,1:02:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.52,1:02:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:48.06,1:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說了不行阿 也幫我吃嘛 我都幫妳吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:27.83,1:03:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:34.24,1:03:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:58.16,1:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了快點冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:05.50,1:04:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:22.05,1:04:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忍不住了 什麼什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.56,1:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:34.46,1:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我放進去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:38.53,1:04:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:42.64,1:04:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忍不住了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:48.81,1:04:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.25,1:05:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舒服嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:13.78,1:08:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:48.37,1:10:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:53.27,1:11:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:01.91,1:12:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.74,1:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:58.33,1:13:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:07.48,1:13:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能射在裡面喔 并託
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:18.48,1:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而官之 我跟姐姐做愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:31.86,1:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出門了 純太 便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:41.70,1:14:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:53.31,1:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 純太
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:01.72,1:15:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:08.50,1:15:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:13.33,1:15:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喝多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:20.27,1:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你忘了這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:25.61,1:15:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:33.05,1:15:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心 那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:58.05,1:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然性愛很麻烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:06.12,1:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好麻煩何 但是回想起來真不錯 姐姐怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:17.50,1:16:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 我 什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.77,1:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 但我就是忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:38.05,1:16:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 這是不對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:46.76,1:16:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再一次就好 我就會把這些忘掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:55.24,1:16:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託別說這種任性的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:03.08,1:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起我都只想自己的事 沒想到妳的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:22.20,1:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純太 很難受嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:28.60,1:17:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:49.82,1:17:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:58.60,1:18:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看純太這麼可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:06.61,1:18:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:14.15,1:18:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 不能做愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:18.95,1:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你了解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:22.39,1:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只可以帮純太做事而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:27.56,1:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐幫我打手槍的條件是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:31.07,1:18:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人在不見面的情况下 只有伸出我的雞雞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:41.68,1:18:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐用手帮我這様打手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:11.97,1:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐這樣可以婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:18.48,1:19:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:22.54,1:20:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 你只有用手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:29.38,1:20:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:45.73,1:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打出來就好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.91,1:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:02.35,1:21:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣嗎 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:33.67,1:22:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:39.15,1:22:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舒服嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:43.15,1:22:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:51.36,1:22:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我幫你舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:48.55,1:23:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐 妳濕了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:57.52,1:24:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也幫你弄濕吧 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:22.87,1:26:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣如何 還要更多嗎 要 我還要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:29.51,1:26:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要再濕一點嘛 我還要再濕一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:44.42,1:27:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐我還要再濕一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:23.92,1:28:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐 我不行了忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:36.37,1:28:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍不住了 可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:46.08,1:28:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:19.91,1:30:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然姐姐幫我打手槍 還是覺得不暢快而失眠
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:34.45,1:30:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐弄的好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:42.73,1:30:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但姐姐也是女人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:51.20,1:30:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐不是也欲求不滿嗎 跟我做愛不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:01.82,1:31:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不行阿 我們有親戚關係阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:16.00,1:31:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是明美回來的日子 也是和姐姐的最後一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:02.48,1:32:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐昨晚累壞了吧
